  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Techniques: Black, Blue, Green, Purple, Red, Perfect </p><p></p><p>You add a mechanism to allow your Puppet Tool to fly.</p><p> How exactly your Puppet Tool's mechanism appears is up to you.</p><p> Your Puppet Tool gains 30 feet of flying speed.</p><p> If your Puppet already has a flying speed, increase its flying speed by +20 feet.</p><p> Effects that would multiply your movement speed, such as the Dash action, multiply your Puppet's flying speed as well.</p><p> For those who practice the Red Technique, two Puppet Tools gain the benefits of this upgrade when you acquire it.</p><p> For those who practice the Purple technique, if your Juggernaut Armor is Weaved Mail or a Wooden Suit, increase the flying speed by +10 feet.</p><p> If it is a Steel Fortress, decrease the flying speed by -10ft.</p><p></p>",
